{"tid":1638601,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國外交部回應央視暫停轉播NBA","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:14:52.000Z","uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb269563c0ba1a26eb3e732942517da3c4c73f0","tid":1638601,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"侯斯頓火箭波士莫雷10月5日發表涉港錯誤言論。7日，NBA總裁肖華表態支持莫雷言論自由嘅權利。央視體育頻道8號宣布即刻暫停NBA賽事轉播。中國外交部發言人耿爽喺當日嘅記者會上表示，中方嘅立場好清楚，建議關註下普通中國群眾對其事嘅反應同佢哋嘅心情。同中方開展交流與合作，唔了解中國嘅民意，呢係行不通嘅。"},{"pid":"f1070c63aa76072099966586deb5df69b60e391c","tid":1638601,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10209f2e0c235cc4e59256dde59f3097fdc3fd0f","tid":1638601,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uuj2zSN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuj2zSN.jpg&h=750d1036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0cf9d4642e7fc759efa258da67024016ca05e7b","tid":1638601,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:09:37.000Z","msg":"你班蝗唔識翻牆睇台灣咩"},{"pid":"ffb3a2e87d142d7b2df0ed1965ca063b8a6b42bc","tid":1638601,"uid":324246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8150f4de360c1709a1632777357829ad0c830d2","tid":1638601,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"恥夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93e4b5b1ec22b2454caa3326ab72542deab2804","tid":1638601,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"屌 睇波都要搵外交部 冇撚野呀"}]}